{"type": "article", "id": 53270, "title": "一款可以站稳的香皂，防滑性能和手感都不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-16T23:20:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 30721, "name": "Anker"}, {"id": 22512, "name": "Good Thing"}, {"id": 50315, "name": "Crosby Studios"}, {"id": 50316, "name": "FURNITURY"}, {"id": 50317, "name": "Teddy Tsoi"}, {"id": 50318, "name": "Daniel Schofield"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 201, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180517000621tapfPGvrUFIibkZl.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Tetra Soap by FURNITURY</h3><p>香港 FURNITURY 团队设计的防滑香皂，也被称作是可以站稳的香皂，它改变了香皂的既有形象。</p><p>肥皂呈波浪形状，提供大量的接触面积以起泡，甚至带有“腿”的形状，让你自然地将肥皂放在肥皂碟上。更重要的是，防波板的形状可以使肥皂保持人体工程学设计，即使它被腐蚀掉，也可以很容易地保存和使用，直到最后一天。早鸟价 120 港币，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1727915872/tetra-soap-a-soap-revolution\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000720GQu9co7SlZ0qLg3I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000720nXpJBZTgx0Vb8Rwd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000721TpXWZdFAs4xLyPvn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000720aRqYWvsDUzEZjk2p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>All-purple Furniture Collection by Crosby Studios</h3><p>Crosby Studios 公司配合夏日音乐节的气氛设计了一组紫色系列家具收藏，抽象的卡通形状带来视觉上的动感，简约线条在不规则的变化下更显出几分童趣。手掌型的落地灯很特别，像要鼓励人们冲上去跟它击击掌。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000757RcO3j2eBqZxQpk4N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170007570PNqIciRg4tGCD59.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170007580rUVlidHW6tIz8h4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000758gPXFqsftxlhLad0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.875635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000758rky7czUvJESNmMFP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.051184\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000758lXyWVI492iwdZbsP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.107868\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000758GRP51CUMvYH9sKSz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/05/15/crosby-studios-all-purple-furniture-collection-hand-shapes-opening-ceremony-collective-concept-nycxdesign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Collection for working from home by Good Thing</h3><p>技术的发展使在家办公成为可能。纽约布鲁克林设计品牌 Good Thing 推出了一系列家具和照明系列产品，针对那些 SOHO 办公的人的需求而设计，包括一个可堆叠的边桌，以及可以制造不同情绪的灯具。参与设计的团队包括 MSDS Studio, Ben Kicic, Jamie Wolfond, Ferréol Babin 和 Earnest Studio。</p><p>最大的亮点就是 Good Thing 创始人 Jamie Wolfond 和纽约设计师 Ben Kicic 的合作作品 Lily 边桌，干净利落的结构之外，可堆叠的特性也给了它更大的发挥空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170008411ds6m3nFKJ9ZW0Ak.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000841BW1hpa2f3L9ryoPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000841i34fNAR0TBleuLmH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714202\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000843M9NGLQkCBatVqYrz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170008434g0pNmc8IYBOWk5Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000843UTVwJEA8vGfr09i4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000844xnqBpdtlKIcQ8YL0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000844149fWaHui5s70clr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Signet by Daniel Schofield</h3><p>英国设计师 Daniel Schofield 设计的这款 Signet 桌子，定位于为游走不定的现代生活与工作方式而设计：人们可能需要定期地改变他们的空间，或频繁地移动。轻盈却牢固的支架使其可以迅速地拆装，因此十分便于存放和运输。</p><p>每个支架可以拆分为两半，并通过两个铝环实现组合及固定。圆环本身包覆着一层软木和橡胶的混合材料，能够紧紧地抓住置于其上的桌面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170009111dpXVNqPQFmgCtGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000911KGHWVcaqf705U9ld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000911z7aRfw25MWBdbZXn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170009129naZ51wpFyvtIOfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170009129pPTGIvoksMEaiXx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000912gpPeMs4kjYuvoB1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000912apTVFIYR5nwuOibM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>D-Sign Light by Teddy Tsoi</h3><p>设计师 Teddy Tsoi 在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上推出了 D-Sign 系列灯具。它最特别的点，在于把灯泡的钨丝变成了变成了比基本线圈更有意义的东西。灯丝勾勒出来的词汇，传递出一些情感和人的关系的价值。</p><p>它不仅可以用作台灯，也可以用作吊灯，最重要的是可以选择自己喜欢的单词，赋予光源意义。早鸟价 155 港币起，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/138087164/d-sign-light-amazing-design-dimmable-led-bulb?\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000944O5DJMgiQaAoC7R6P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664762\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000944kiNKoecMGTPZ7t1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000944CeK4NwvbBmtSDoiP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805170009466rkxCTs4w7dZX1yN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000946MxVWqg1P4Lv3eJnS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000946MC4QkXjWARVZIlUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.847619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517000946jHasqRvwVpl8KkEc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nebula by Anker 智能微投</h3><p>Nebula 是 Anker 母公司旗下的创新影音娱乐品牌。Nebula 智能微型投影仪是其推出的一款采用智能手机处理器的投影仪，它同时拿到了 2018 年的红点设计奖和 iF 设计奖。</p><p>它集合了安卓 7.1 平板电脑、360°蓝牙音箱、便携投影仪三种功能。重约 470 克的可乐罐大小身型，赋予其便携属性，无线投屏功能最大可投射 100 吋画面，还可以一键切换蓝牙音箱，支持 4 小时本地视频播放，30 小时 HiFi 音乐，边充边用不用断电。</p><p>此外，即将面世的红色升级版本，还将拥有今年俄罗斯世界杯的点播权。售价 2099 元，<a href=\"https://item.jd.com/6371256.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517001026vyBzoMJ6DfEPn2ig.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517001026chYMo3nyiztxTVQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517001026M27zFGCaLwmlDHdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562590\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517001026DdOZuCB8i3pq5fmF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517001026zhDiA6lkLVIgy8Fa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562590\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517001026YK9He7Bq26WvxpFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}